<p>&quot;now sitting on sofa&quot;</p>
<p>Should this be &quot;now sitting on <em>the</em> sofa&quot;?</p>
<p>Also, liked the tale. Little bit confused about it. Like, Martha is acting as if the river effect was her idea, but the end implies that it wasn't her idea.</p>
<p>Was it just a coincidence that a member of AWCY came across another's creation and then accidentally took credit? Or am I understanding it wrong?</p>
<p>Aside from that, really like the tale. Always love seeing AWCY stuff, and this is a fantastic look into their process and intentions.</p>

