														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2280241">
									

<p>Endearing and engaging. What I loved the most is the idea that Martha seems to be a willing agent of an anomalous something, while accepting that something's nature and not its oddness. Is it a pervading memetic/cognitive/infohazardous abnormality, an entity which may as well be considered normal and symbiotic to humanity or even a Jungian manifestation of humanity as a creating force, with the Flow being its center?</p>
<p>Maybe I'm reading far too much into it, but I love coming to this site because of tales such as this. The pic only helps round up an already polished jewel. Very good work, Sunny. :3</p>
<p>+1</p>

